  <facts><![CDATA[<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Good to know</strong></p>
<p><strong>Hiking trails:</strong> 100km in Arinsal</p>
<p><strong>Terrain:</strong> Mountain terrain</p>
<p><strong>Best time to go:</strong> June, July &amp; August. Enjoy cool air at the top of the mountains but head back to resort for the Pyrenees sunshine</p>
<p><strong>Recommended for:</strong> <span>New walkers, regular walkers, experienced hikers, families with kids, families with teens</span></p>
<p><strong>Fly into:</strong> Barcelona airport</p>
<p><strong>Fly from:</strong> London Gatwick, London Heathrow, Luton, Birmingham and Manchester</p>]]></facts>
